name: El/La Para TransLatinas
description: Free community support, immigration help, and advocacy for trans Latina women
fullDescription: El/La Para TransLatinas provides community building, protection, and support services specifically for transgender Latina women in the Bay Area.
whatTheyOffer:
- Community support groups
- Immigration assistance
- Health navigation
- Safety and advocacy
- Leadership development
- Know Your Rights workshops
- Cultural programming
howToGetIt:
1. Contact El/La Para TransLatinas
2. Join community groups and events
3. Access support services
4. Participate in workshops
5. Services in Spanish and English
keywords: El/La Para TransLatinas, San Francisco, transgender, trans Latina, Latina, immigration, health navigation, know your rights, leadership, community support
